PORTLAND, Ore. -- It's the second-to-last week of the high school football regular season so league titles and playoff spots are up for grabs. With that, there was no shortage of great games. 
Here's our full coverage plan for Week 8 of Friday Night Flights. 
KGW's Game of the Week 
KGW's Game of the Week is McNary at No. 6 South Salem! The undefeated Saxons can clinch at least a share of the Greater Valley Conference league title with a win. 
We'll have photos and full highlights from the game. Chunky, McKinzie & Jake from 98.7 The Bull will be at the game to present the Game of the Week Game Ball. 
Follow KGW HS Sports on Twitter for updates on the game.
